  "texts": [
    "In these experiments we simply used our OOD test set consisting of 7 relations unseen during fine-tuning (see §A).",
    "When we perform the analysis discussed in §4.1 and §4.2, we additionally evaluated the models on the OOD test set.",
    "For completeness, we add here Figure 8, which is the out-of-distribution version of Figure 3.",
    "The corresponding in-distribution results (Figure 3b) were discussed in §4.2.",
    "We notice that similar trends, just with a smaller overall magnitude of the performance drop, up to 6 points drop compared to up to 14 for in-distribution."
  ]
}